'''磷酸二氫銣'''是一種[[無機化合物|無機化合物]]，屬於磷酸二氢鹽，化學式為RbH<sub>2</sub>PO<sub>4</sub>，是[[銣|銣]]的磷酸酸式盐之一。<ref>Sotnikova-Yuzhik, V. A.; Prodan, E. A.; Peslyak, G. V. Rubidium dihydrotriphosphate. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1990. 35 (4): 849-852. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>

== 制備 ==
磷酸二氫銣可由[[碳酸铷|碳酸铷]]和[[磷酸|磷酸]]按Rb:PO<sub>4</sub>摩尔比1:1反应得到：<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Solid State Ionics|volume=211|language=en|date=2012-03|pages=34–41|doi=10.1016/j.ssi.2012.01.011|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0167273812000240|title=Effects of porous SiO2 on protonic conductivity of RbH2PO4-based composite electrolytes|accessdate=2020-04-19|author=Zikun Li, Tongbor Tang}}</ref>
: Rb<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub> + 2 H<sub>3</sub>PO<sub>4</sub> → 2 RbH<sub>2</sub>PO<sub>4</sub> + CO<sub>2</sub>↑ + H<sub>2</sub>O
加入[[甲醇|甲醇]]后，产物析出，过滤并于80 °C干燥。

== 性质 ==
磷酸二氫銣在238 °C开始分解：<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Thermochimica Acta|volume=501|issue=1-2|language=en|date=2010-03|pages=59–64|doi=10.1016/j.tca.2010.01.010|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0040603110000183|title=High-temperature thermal behaviors of XH2PO4 (X=Cs, Rb, K, Na) and LiH2PO3|accessdate=2020-04-19|author=Zikun Li, Tongbor Tang}}</ref>
: RbH<sub>2</sub>PO<sub>4</sub> → RbPO<sub>3</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O

